## Data Sources

| Source | Type | Volume | Description |
|--------|------|--------|-------------|
| M5 Forecasting (Kaggle/Walmart) | **REAL** | 58.3M rows | Daily sales for 30,490 SKU-store combinations, 2011–2016 |
| Open-Meteo Historical Weather | **REAL** | ~19,690 rows | Daily weather for CA, TX, WI states |
| FRED Macroeconomic Data | **REAL** | ~500 rows | CPI, unemployment, consumer sentiment, oil price |
| Inventory & Orders | **SYNTHETIC** | Generated | Lead times, safety stock, order policies (see disclaimer) |

