## Synthetic Data Disclaimer

**The demand signal is REAL** (Walmart M5 public dataset). **The inventory layer is SYNTHETIC.**

Inventory parameters (lead times, holding costs, order costs, supplier data, stockout events) are generated from calibrated statistical distributions to produce realistic operational behavior. They are not real Walmart operational data.

Every output derived from synthetic parameters is labeled `SYNTHETIC` in code, JSON assets, and the frontend dashboard. See [docs/08_synthetic_data_disclaimer.md](docs/08_synthetic_data_disclaimer.md) for full methodology.

