## Project Structure

```
retail-demand-intelligence/
├── src/
│   ├── ingest/          # M5, weather, macro data ingestion
│   ├── transform/       # Bronze -> Silver transformations
│   ├── classification/  # ADI/CV2, ABC/XYZ, SCD Type 2
│   ├── features/        # Feature store (8 families, leakage guard)
│   ├── models/          # LightGBM, baselines, training, prediction
│   ├── reconciliation/  # Hierarchical reconciliation (MinT-Shrink)
│   ├── evaluation/      # Backtesting, metrics, segmented report
│   ├── inventory/       # Monte Carlo, newsvendor, policy comparator
│   ├── export/          # JSON serving asset export
│   └── monitoring/      # Drift detection, CUSUM, alert engine
├── app/                 # React + TypeScript + Tailwind dashboard
├── docs/                # Architecture, runbooks, model cards
├── tests/               # 795 tests (unit + integration + e2e)
├── configs/             # YAML configuration files
├── contracts/           # Data contracts (Pandera schemas)
├── sql/                 # dbt models and snapshots
└── .github/workflows/   # CI/CD pipelines
```

